VALUES
  (22174, 28, 5, 13, 'When Ephraim saw his sickness, and Judah saw his wound, then went Ephraim to the Assyrian, and sent to king Jareb: yet could he not heal you, nor cure you of your wound.', '1~0669~ 2~07200~ 4~02483~, 6~03063~ [7] 9~04205~, 11~03212~ 12~0669~ 15~0804~, 17~07971~ 19~04428~ 20~03377~ 21~07378~:* 23~03201~ 26~07495~ 29~01455~ 33~04205~.'),
  (7852, 9, 24, 6, 'And he said unto his men, The LORD forbid that I should do this thing unto my master, the LORD''S anointed, to stretch forth mine hand against him, seeing he is the anointed of the LORD.', '2~0559~ 5~0582~, 7~03068~ 8~02486~ 12~06213~ 14~01697~ 17~0113~, 19~03068~ 20~04899~, 23~07971~ 25~03027~ [30] 32~04899~ 35~03068~.'),
